Shortcut (NERDTree) toggle tree visibility
      \ nnoremap <silent> <Space>td :NERDTreeToggle<CR>

Shortcut (NERDTree) open tree and focus it
      \ nnoremap <silent> <Space>ed :NERDTreeFocus<CR>

Shortcut (NERDTree) find current buffer in tree
      \ nnoremap <silent> <Space>eD :NERDTreeFind<CR>

Shortcut (NERDTree) refresh tree from root node
      \ nnoremap <silent> <Space>rd :NERDTreeRefreshRoot<CR>
